                            <comment id="71602" author="mark.pollack" created="Sat, 9 Apr 2011 09:43:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The error message in the driver is a bit unclear.  The com.mongodb.DB object is tracking calls to authenticate.  If authentication has succeeded one before, additional attempts to authenticate will throw the error indicated in the title of the issue.  same &quot;DBObject&quot; should read instead &quot;same com.mongodb.DB instance&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
